1a354084-772d-4980-9b19-9fc05b1aa519.do_description: To make the output, you have to...move the bars into colors
1a354084-772d-4980-9b19-9fc05b1aa519.grid_description: The output grid size...same size as the input
1a354084-772d-4980-9b19-9fc05b1aa519.see_description: In the input, you should see...black grid with two colors

b5dfa68d-928c-441f-a1e2-17c951684a69.do_description: To make the output, you have to...move the red boxes up into the blue pattern to fill the black spaces.
b5dfa68d-928c-441f-a1e2-17c951684a69.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input.
b5dfa68d-928c-441f-a1e2-17c951684a69.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black grid with a blue pattern on top and red boxes toward the bottom.

cf851ef2-88b7-42a6-8701-522f83dbff42.do_description: To make the output, you have to...imagine the blue is a vacuum and sucks the red up into the open spaces.  Move all red straight up.
cf851ef2-88b7-42a6-8701-522f83dbff42.grid_description: The output grid size...same as the input
cf851ef2-88b7-42a6-8701-522f83dbff42.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black grid with a blue pattern across the top and red at the bottom
